@node faqs "Frequently asked questions"

Q:	What's a default project and how do I create it?

A:	A  default  project  is  from BareED's point of view an empty document but with a valid icon (project
	icon).
	BareED  can save such a default to disk in case no characters are in BareED's text buffer. But you
	can choose colours, font and so on.
	These characteristics will be saved along with the icon to disk - whilst the text file won't be saved!
	A double click now on this icon brings up BareED who tries to display these saved characteristics.

@{fg shine}_______________________________________________________________________________________@{fg shadow}
ŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻ@{fg text}

Q:	How can I insert return and tab keys in Find&Replace window ? (\\n \\t in PageLiner)

A	Use the standard OS short cuts:
		CTRL + left AMIGA + j	- insert linefeed into current string at current position
		CTRL + left AMIGA + m	- insert carriage-return into current string at current position
		CTRL + left AMIGA + TAB	- insert tab into current string at current position

@{fg shine}_______________________________________________________________________________________@{fg shadow}
ŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻ@{fg text}

Q:	How  do  I  convert  a plain DOS / Windows text file (there are at line end several non-displayable
	characters)?

A:	Open the Find / Replace requester.
	Enter as find string:
		CTRL + left AMIGA + m
	Leave the replace string empty and select "Replace All".

@{fg shine}_______________________________________________________________________________________@{fg shadow}
