Q:	Why can't I mark with the mouse characters from bottom to top?
Q:	Why when I start to mark a block, if I go back to initial position it lost my mark session ?

A:	Up  from version 0.9893 of BareED marking a range of characters is supported from bottom upwards
	although personally I don't like it!

