Q:	BareED does print out in the selected font, however but only print in black (not colour).
	Isn't that a bug?

A:	No,  BareED  makes  use  of  a  plug-in  in  order  to  print  out  texts.  However, this plug-in does
	currently only allow print outs to be made in monochrome.

